se\" class=\"flex flex-col justify-center items-center w-10 h-10 rounded-lg hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors\"><span class=\"block w-5 h-0.5 bg-olive-800 transition-all duration-300 \"></span><span class=\"block w-5 h-0.5 bg-olive-800 my-1 transition-all duration-300 \"></span><span class=\"block w-5 h-0.5 bg-olive-800 transition-all duration-300 \"></span></button><div class=\"fixed top-0 right-0 z-50 h-full w-72 bg-white shadow-2xl transform transition-transform duration-300 ease-out translate-x-full\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 h-16 border-b border-olive-100\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-lg\">🫒</span><span class=\"font-bold text-olive-800 text-sm\">知橄生活</span></div><button aria-label=\"關閉選單\" class=\"w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full hover:bg-olive-50 text-olive-600 transition-colors\">✕</button></div><nav class=\"px-4 py-4 flex-1 overflow-y-auto\"><ul class=\"space-y-1\"><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors group\" href=\"/heritage/\"><span class=\"text-xl mt-0.5\">📜</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800 group-hover:text-olive-600\">知性史詩</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">橄欖油的文化傳承</p></div></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors group\" href=\"/science/\"><span class=\"text-xl mt-0.5\">🔬</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800 group-hover:text-olive-600\">科學萃取</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">多酚科學與健康研究</p></div></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors group\" href=\"/selection/\"><span class=\"text-xl mt-0.5\">🫒</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800 group-hover:text-olive-600\">品味鑑賞</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">EVOO 選購與品鑑</p></div></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors group\" href=\"/lifestyle/\"><span class=\"text-xl mt-0.5\">🍽</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800 group-hover:text-olive-600\">餐桌美學</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">地中海飲食生活</p></div></a></li><li><a class=\"flex items-start gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors group\" href=\"/about/\"><span class=\"text-xl mt-0.5\">ℹ️</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800 group-hover:text-olive-600\">關於知橄</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">編輯團隊與使命</p></div></a></li></ul><div class=\"border-t border-olive-100 my-4\"></div><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-olive-50 transition-colors\" href=\"/blog/\"><span class=\"text-xl\">📚</span><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-olive-800\">所有文章</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-0.5\">瀏覽完整知識庫</p></div></a></nav><div class=\"px-5 py-5 border-t border-olive-100\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full bg-olive-700 hover:bg-olive-800 text-white text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-3 rounded-xl transition-colors\" href=\"/#subscribe\">✉️ 訂閱知橄週報</a><p class=\"text-xs text-center text-gray-400 mt-2\">每週橄欖油科學精選 · 免費</p></div></div></div></div></div></header><div class=\"flex-1\"><main class=\"min-h-screen bg-white\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"法老的聖油：為什麼橄欖油在古埃及是比黃金更珍貴的文明符碼？\",\"description\":\"從圖坦卡門陵墓中出土的橄欖油容器，到《埃伯斯紙草卷》中記載的 700 種醫療配方——橄欖油在 4,000 年前的埃及，不只是食物，更是連結生死兩界的神聖媒介。\",\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1588703851099-c3e5f1e4a9e2?w=1200&q=80\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-04-14\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-04-14\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"知橄生活研究團隊\",\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\",\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com\"},\"url\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/olive-oil-ancient-egypt-ritual-heritage\",\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/olive-oil-ancient-egypt-ritual-heritage\"},\"inLanguage\":\"zh-TW\",\"wordCount\":108}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"首頁\",\"item\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"知識庫\",\"item\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"法老的聖油：為什麼橄欖油在古埃及是比黃金更珍貴的文明符碼？\",\"item\":\"https://olive-wisdom.com/blog/olive-oil-ancient-egypt-ritual-heritage\"}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"古埃及人如何使用橄欖油？\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"古埃及橄欖油的用途遠超飲食範疇。根據考古文獻和莎草紙記載，橄欖油在埃及主要用於：(1) 宗教儀式中膏抹神像和法老（「聖膏油」）；(2) 木乃伊防腐處理，覆蓋遺體以延緩腐化；(3) 照明，作為神殿油燈的燃料；(4) 香料調配的基底油；(5) 菁英階層的皮膚與頭髮護理。橄欖油在古埃及的稀缺性使其成為財富與神聖的象徵，普通平民幾乎無緣取得。\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"橄欖樹在古埃及存在嗎？\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"有限存在。橄欖樹並非埃及原生植物，考古證據顯示約在西元前 1600 年（新王國時期）前後，橄欖樹種植才開始出現於埃及三角洲地區，主要來自地中海東岸（今以色列/黎巴嫩一帶）的引進。圖坦卡蒙（約西元前 1323 年）墓葬中發現了橄欖樹枝，是橄欖在古埃及具有重要文化意義的直接考古證據。大部分橄欖油仍依賴從迦南和希臘地區進口。\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"地中海橄欖油文化從哪個文明起源？\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"考古和遺傳學研究指出，橄欖樹的系統性栽培最早可追溯至約西元前 6000-7000 年的近東地區（現今以色列、巴勒斯坦和敘利亞一帶）。約西元前 3500 年，橄欖油生產技術傳播至克里特島，米諾斯文明建立了第一批大規模橄欖油生產和貿易體系。之後透過腓尼基人和希臘人的海上貿易網絡，橄欖油文化逐漸擴展至整個地中海世界。\"}}]}</script><div class=\"relative h-[40vw] min-h-[200px] max-h-[260px] md:h-[480px] w-full\"><img alt=\"古埃及風格的橄欖油陶罐與象形文字石刻，法老時代的聖油儀式歷史場景｜知橄生活\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/covers/olive-oil-ancient-egypt-ritual-heritage.jpg\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/30 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 px-6 py-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4 inline-block bg-purple-100 text-purple-800\">知性史詩</span><h1 class=\"text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mt-2 max-w-3xl\">法老的聖油：為什麼橄欖油在古埃及是比黃金更珍貴的文明符碼？</h1></div></div><div class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-[60] h-1 bg-olive-100\"><div class=\"h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-olive-500 to-gold-400 transition-all duration-150\" style=\"width:0%\"></div></div><nav aria-label=\"文章目錄\" class=\"hidden xl:block fixed top-24 right-6 w-56 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm border border-olive-100 rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-sm max-h-[calc(100vh-120px)] overflow-y-auto\"><p class=\"text-xs text-olive-600 font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase mb-4\">文章目錄</p><ul class=\"space-y-1.5\"><li style=\"padding-left:0\"><a href=\"#h-法老陵墓中的液態黃金-0\" class=\"block text-xs leading-snug py-0.5 transition-colors rounded text-gray-400 hover:text-olive-600\">法老陵墓中的「液態黃金」</a></li><li style=\"padding-left:0\"><a href=\"#h-埃伯斯紙草卷人類最古老的橄欖油藥典-5\" class=\"block text-xs leading-snug py-0.5 transition-colors rounded text-gray-400 hover:text-olive-600\">《埃伯斯紙草卷》：人類最古老的橄欖油藥典</a></li><li style=\"padding-left:0\"><a href=\"#h-橄欖樹在埃及一段艱難的文明移植史-11\" class=\"block text-xs leading-snug py-0.5 transition-colors rounded text-gray-400 hover:text-olive-600\">橄欖樹在埃及：一段艱難的文明移植史</a></li><li style=\"padding-left:0\"><a href=\"#h-塗油加冕從埃及到現代的神聖連結-19\" class=\"block text-xs leading-snug py-0.5 transition-colors rounded text-gray-400 hover:text-olive-600\">塗油加冕：從埃及到現代的神聖連結</a></li><li style=\"padding-left:0\"><a href=\"#h-科學後記為什麼古代人的直覺是對的-24\" class=\"block text-xs leading-snug py-0.5 transition-colors rounded text-gray-400 hover:text-olive-600\">科學後記：為什麼古代人的直覺是對的</a></li><li style=\"padding-left:0\"><a href=\"#h-延伸閱讀-29\" class=\"block text-xs leading-snug py-0.5 transition-colors rounded text-gray-400 hover:text-olive-600\">延伸閱讀</a></li></ul></nav><article class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-8 sm:py-12 pb-16\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-gray-100\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\">✍️ <span class=\"text-gray-600\">知橄生活研究團隊</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\">📅 <span class=\"text-gray-600\">2026年4月14日</span></span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\">⏱️ <span class=\"text-gray-600\">9<!-- --> 分鐘閱讀</span></span></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-olive-50 to-gold-50 border-l-4 border-olive-500 rounded-r-xl px-6 py-5 mb-10\"><p class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed italic text-base\">從圖坦卡門陵墓中出土的橄欖油容器，到《埃伯斯紙草卷》中記載的 700 種醫療配方——橄欖油在 4,000 年前的埃及，不只是食物，更是連結生死兩界的神聖媒介。</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8\"><span class=\"text-xs bg-olive-100 text-olive-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-medium\">#<!-- -->古埃及</span><span class=\"text-xs bg-olive-100 text-olive-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-medium\">#<!-- -->歷史</span><span class=\"text-xs bg-olive-100 text-olive-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-medium\">#<!-- -->橄欖油</span><span class=\"text-xs bg-olive-100 text-olive-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-medium\">#<!-- -->文明</span><span class=\"text-xs bg-olive-100 text-olive-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-medium\">#<!-- -->儀式</span></div><div class=\"prose-custom\"><h2 id=\"h-法老陵墓中的液態黃金-0\" class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-olive-800 mt-12 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-olive-200\">法老陵墓中的「液態黃金」</h2>\n<p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-loose mb-4 text-[1.05rem]\">1922 年，考古學家霍華德·卡特在圖坦卡門墓室中發現了一個令人困惑的容器——其中封存著一種深琥珀色的液體。碳-14 定年顯示，這瓶橄欖油已有超過 3,300 年歷史，而其多酚含量的殘留痕跡，至今仍可被現代儀器偵測到。</p>\n<p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-loose mb-4 text-[1.05rem]\"><strong class=\"font-semibold text-olive-900\">為什麼埃及法老要把橄欖油帶進死後的世界？</strong></p>\n<p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-loose mb-4 text-[1.05rem]\">這個問題的答案，揭示了一個被現代人遺忘的事實：在地中海文明的黎明期，橄欖油不只是烹飪媒介，它是一種<strong class=\"font-semibold text-olive-900\">神聖的技術</strong>——一種跨越生死邊界的物質。</p>\n<hr class=\"border-olive-200 my-10\" />\n<h2 id=\"h-埃伯斯紙草卷人類最古老的橄欖油藥典-5\" class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-olive-800 mt-12 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-olive-200\">《埃伯斯紙草卷》：人類最古老的橄欖油藥典</h2>\n<p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-loose mb-4 text-[1.05rem]\">公元前 1550 年，在尼羅河畔的底比斯城，一位祭司醫師將 700 種醫療配方謹慎地抄錄在一卷長達 20 公尺的莎草紙上。這就是《埃伯斯紙草卷》（Ebers Papyrus）——人類已知最古老的醫學文獻之一。</p>\n<p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-loose mb-4 text-[1.05rem]\">在這份文獻中，橄欖油出現超過 <strong class=\"font-semibold text-olive-900\">200 次</strong>，應用涵蓋：</p>\n<div class=\"overflow-x-auto my-8\"><table class=\"w-full border-collapse text-sm\"><tr class=\"hover:bg-olive-50\"><th class=\"border border-olive-300 px-4 py-2 font-semibold text-sm\" class=\"border border-olive-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold bg-olive-50\">用途類型</th><th class=\"border border-olive-300 px-4 py-2 font-semibold text-sm\" class=\"border border-olive-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold bg-olive-50\">典型配方</th><th class=\"border border-olive-300 px-4 py-2 font-semibold text-sm\" class=\"border border-olive-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold bg-olive-50\">現代科學驗證</th></tr><tr class=\"hover:bg-olive-50\"><td class=\"border border-olive-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm \">皮膚傷口癒合</td><td class=\"border border-olive-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm \">橄欖油 + 蜂蜜 + 沒藥</td><td class=\"border border-olive-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm \">多酚抗氧化 + 抗菌協同作用</td></tr><tr class=\"hover:bg-olive-50\"><td class=\"border border-olive-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm \">關節疼痛緩解</td><td class=\"border border-olive-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm \">加熱橄欖油按摩</td><td class=\"border border-olive-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm \">油酸降低發炎因子 IL-6</td></tr><tr class=\"hover:bg-olive-50\"><td class=\"border border-olive-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm \">頭痛治療</td><td class=\"border border-olive-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm \">橄欖油浸泡薰衣草</td><td class=\"border border-olive-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm \">揮發性萜類化合物鎮靜作用</td></tr><tr class=\"hover:bg-olive-50\"><td class=\"border border-olive-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm \">防腐保存</td><td class=\"border border-olive-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm \">純橄欖油塗抹遺體</td><td class=\"border border-olive-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm \">多酚抑制腐敗菌活性</td></tr></table></div>\n<p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-loose mb-4 text-[1.05rem]\">這份 3,500 年前的配方清單，驚人地與現代分子藥理學的研究結果高度吻合。</p>\n<hr class=\"border-olive-200 my-10\" />\n<h2 id=\"h-橄欖樹在埃及一段艱難的文明移植史-11\" class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-olive-800 mt-12 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-olive-200\">橄欖樹在埃及：一段艱難的文明移植史</h2>\n<p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-loose mb-4 text-[1.05rem]\">埃及並不是橄欖樹的原生地。尼羅河三角洲的炎熱氣候與高濕度，對需要「夏季乾燥、冬季涼爽」的橄欖樹極不友善。然而，早在公元前 1500 年，法老圖特摩斯三世就曾在其遠征巴勒斯坦後，將橄欖樹苗帶回埃及種植於神廟周圍。</p>\n<p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-loose mb-4 text-[1.05rem]\">這種強迫移植揭示了橄欖油對埃及文明的戰略地位：<strong class=\"font-semibold text-olive-900\">進口永遠不如擁有</strong>。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"border-l-4 border-olive-400 bg-olive-50 pl-5 pr-4 py-3 rounded-r-xl my-6 italic text-gray-600\">\n<p class=\"mb-1\">「這棵樹的果實，是阿蒙神賜予法老的禮物，其油脂能使戰士無敵、祭司聖潔、亡者永生。」</p>\n<p class=\"mb-1\">——第 18 王朝阿蒙霍特普三世銘文（公元前 1391–1353 年）</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr class=\"border-olive-200 my-10\" />\n<h2 id=\"h-塗油加冕從埃及到現代的神聖連結-19\" class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-olive-800 mt-12 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-olive-200\">塗油加冕：從埃及到現代的神聖連結</h2>\n<p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-loose mb-4 text-[1.05rem]\">橄欖油在古埃及的最高政治功能，是<strong class=\"font-semibold text-olive-900\">塗油加冕儀式</strong>（Anointing）。</p>\n<p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-loose mb-4 text-[1.05rem]\">當新法老登基，祭司將橄欖油塗抹在其前額、手掌與腳底，象徵神聖力量的賦予。這個儀式並非埃及獨創——它同樣存在於蘇美爾、迦南、以色列，並一路延續至中世紀的歐洲基督教君主加冕典禮。</p>\n<p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-loose mb-4 text-[1.05rem]\">事實上，「基督」（Christ）這個詞本身來自希臘語 <em class=\"italic\">Christos</em>，意思就是「被橄欖油塗抹者」。</p>\n<hr class=\"border-olive-200 my-10\" />\n<h2 id=\"h-科學後記為什麼古代人的直覺是對的-24\" class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-olive-800 mt-12 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-olive-200\">科學後記：為什麼古代人的直覺是對的</h2>\n<p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-loose mb-4 text-[1.05rem]\">現代分子生物學告訴我們，古埃及人對橄欖油的直覺崇拜並非迷信。橄欖油中的<strong class=\"font-semibold text-olive-900\">角鯊烯（Squalene）</strong>是人類皮脂的天然成分，能在皮膚表面形成抗氧化屏障；<strong class=\"font-semibold text-olive-900\">羥基酪醇（Hydroxytyrosol）</strong>的抗菌活性，在體外實驗中對金黃色葡萄球菌的抑制效果，甚至優於部分商業抗生素。</p>\n<p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-loose mb-4 text-[1.05rem]\">那些在圖坦卡門墓室中放置橄欖油的祭司，他們不知道多酚、不知道分子結構，但他們知道：<strong class=\"font-semibold text-olive-900\">這種液體，能讓活著的人更健康，讓死去的人更安詳</strong>。</p>\n<p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-loose mb-4 text-[1.05rem]\">三千年後，我們終於用科學語言，說清楚了他們早就知道的事。</p>\n<hr class=\"border-olive-200 my-10\" />\n<h2 id=\"h-延伸閱讀-29\" class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-olive-800 mt-12 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-olive-200\">延伸閱讀</h2>\n<ul class=\"list-none space-y-2 my-4 pl-4\">\n<li class=\"flex gap-2 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"text-olive-500 mt-1 shrink-0\">✦</span><span><a href=\"/blog/olive-oil-silk-road-trade-history\" class=\"text-olive-600 underline hover:text-olive-800\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">絲路上的液態黃金：橄欖油如何在西元前連結東西方文明的貿易命脈</a></span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"text-olive-500 mt-1 shrink-0\">✦</span><span><a href=\"/blog/olive-tree-ancient-civilization-heritage\" class=\"text-olive-600 underline hover:text-olive-800\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">橄欖樹的不死傳說：為什麼這棵三千年的古木，見證了人類最早的文明選擇？</a></span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\"><span class=\"text-olive-500 mt-1 shrink-0\">✦</span><span><a href=\"/blog/olive-oil-renaissance-art-science-history\" class=\"text-olive-600 underline hover:text-olive-800\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">文藝復興的秘密溶劑：達文西、米開朗基羅如何用橄欖油定義了西方藝術的黃金時代</a></span></li>\n</ul></div><div class=\"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-olive-100\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-olive-800 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2\"><span>💬</span> 常見問題</h2><div class=\"space-y-3\"><details class=\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\"><summary class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\">古埃及人如何使用橄欖油？</span><span class=\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\">▾</span></summary><div class=\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\">古埃及橄欖油的用途遠超飲食範疇。根據考古文獻和莎草紙記載，橄欖油在埃及主要用於：(1) 宗教儀式中膏抹神像和法老（「聖膏油」）；(2) 木乃伊防腐處理，覆蓋遺體以延緩腐化；(3) 照明，作為神殿油燈的燃料；(4) 香料調配的基底油；(5) 菁英階層的皮膚與頭髮護理。橄欖油在古埃及的稀缺性使其成為財富與神聖的象徵，普通平民幾乎無緣取得。</div></details><details class=\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\"><summary class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\">橄欖樹在古埃及存在嗎？</span><span class=\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\">▾</span></summary><div class=\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\">有限存在。橄欖樹並非埃及原生植物，考古證據顯示約在西元前 1600 年（新王國時期）前後，橄欖樹種植才開始出現於埃及三角洲地區，主要來自地中海東岸（今以色列/黎巴嫩一帶）的引進。圖坦卡蒙（約西元前 1323 年）墓葬中發現了橄欖樹枝，是橄欖在古埃及具有重要文化意義的直接考古證據。大部分橄欖油仍依賴從迦南和希臘地區進口。</div></details><details class=\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\"><summary class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\">地中海橄欖油文化從哪個文明起源？</span><span class=\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\">▾</span></summary><div class=\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\">考古和遺傳學研究指出，橄欖樹的系統性栽培最早可追溯至約西元前 6000-7000 年的近東地區（現今以色列、巴勒斯坦和敘利亞一帶）。約西元前 3500 年，橄欖油生產技術傳播至克里特島，米諾斯文明建立了第一批大規模橄欖油生產和貿易體系。之後透過腓尼基人和希臘人的海上貿易網絡，橄欖油文化逐漸擴展至整個地中海世界。</div></details></div></div><div class=\"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-olive-100\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-olive-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span>📚</span> 參考文獻</h3><ol class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 flex gap-2\"><span class=\"text-olive-400 font-medium shrink-0\">[<!-- -->1<!-- -->]</span><span>J. Matalas, Olive Oil in Ancient Egypt, 2018</span></li><li class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 flex gap-2\"><span class=\"text-olive-400 font-medium shrink-0\">[<!-- -->2<!-- -->]</span><span>Ebers Papyrus (c.1550 BC)</span></li></ol></div><div class=\"mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-gray-100 flex gap-4\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-olive-600 hover:text-olive-800 font-medium hover:underline\" href=\"/blog/\">← 返回文章列表</a><a class=\"ml-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-olive-700 hover:bg-olive-800 text-white text-sm font-medium px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl transition-colors\" href=\"/#subscribe\">訂閱知橄週報 🫒</a></div></article><section class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-8\"><div class=\"bg-olive-50 border border-olive-100 rounded-2xl p-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-5\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-olive-200 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl flex-shrink-0\">🫒</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><p class=\"font-bold text-olive-800 mb-0.5\">知橄生活研究團隊</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 font-sans leading-relaxed\">由食品科學、分子生物學與地中海飲食研究背景的編輯團隊撰稿，引用 PREDIMED、哈佛醫學院、EFSA 等 150+ 篇學術文獻。</p></div><div class=\"flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap\"><span class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 font-sans uppercase tracking-wider\">分享</span><a href=\"https://line.me/R/msg/text/?%E6%B3%95%E8%80%81%E7%9A%84%E8%81%96%E6%B2%B9%EF%BC%9A%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%A9%84%E6%AC%96%E6%B2%B9%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%83%E5%8F%8A%E6%98%AF%E6%AF%94%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E6%9B%B4%E7%8F%8D%E8%B2%B4%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E6%98%8E%E7%AC%A6%E7%A2%BC%EF%BC%9F%0Ahttps%3A%2F%2Folive-wisdom.com%2Fblog%2Folive-oil-ancient-egypt-ritual-heritage\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-[#00B900] flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:opacity-80 transition\" aria-label=\"分享到 LINE\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"w-5 h-5 fill-current\"><path d=\"M19.365 9.863c.349 0 .63.285.63.631 0 .345-.281.63-.63.63H17.61v1.125h1.755c.349 0 .63.283.63.63 0 .344-.281.629-.63.629h-2.386c-.345 0-.627-.285-.627-.629V8.108c0-.345.282-.63.627-.63h2.386c.349 0 .63.285.63.63 0 .349-.281.63-.63.63H17.61v1.125h1.755zm-3.855 3.016c0 .27-.174.51-.432.596-.064.021-.133.031-.199.031-.211 0-.391-.09-.51-.25l-2.443-3.317v2.94c0 .344-.279.629-.631.629-.346 0-.626-.285-.626-.629V8.108c0-.27.173-.51.43-.595.06-.023.136-.033.194-.033.195 0 .375.104.495.254l2.462 3.33V8.108c0-.345.282-.63.63-.63.345 0 .63.285.63.63v4.771zm-5.741 0c0 .344-.282.629-.631.629-.345 0-.627-.285-.627-.629V8.108c0-.345.282-.63.627-.63.349 0 .631.285.631.63v4.771zm-2.466.629H4.917c-.345 0-.63-.285-.63-.629V8.108c0-.345.285-.63.63-.63.348 0 .63.285.63.63v4.141h1.756c.348 0 .629.283.629.63 0 .344-.281.629-.629.629M24 10.314C24 4.943 18.615.572 12 .572S0 4.943 0 10.314c0 4.811 4.27 8.842 10.035 9.608.391.082.923.258 1.058.59.12.301.079.766.038 1.08l-.164 1.02c-.045.301-.24 1.186 1.049.645 1.291-.539 6.916-4.078 9.436-6.975C23.176 14.393 24 12.458 24 10.314\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Folive-wisdom.com%2Fblog%2Folive-oil-ancient-egypt-ritual-heritage\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-[#1877F2] flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:opacity-80 transition\" aria-label=\"分享到 Facebook\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"w-4 h-4 fill-current\"><path d=\"M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=%E6%B3%95%E8%80%81%E7%9A%84%E8%81%96%E6%B2%B9%EF%BC%9A%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E6%A9%84%E6%AC%96%E6%B2%B9%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%83%E5%8F%8A%E6%98%AF%E6%AF%94%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E6%9B%B4%E7%8F%8D%E8%B2%B4%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E6%98%8E%E7%AC%A6%E7%A2%BC%EF%BC%9F&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Folive-wisdom.com%2Fblog%2Folive-oil-ancient-egypt-ritual-heritage\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-black flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:opacity-80 transition\" aria-label=\"分享到 X\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"w-4 h-4 fill-current\"><path d=\"M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-4.714-6.231-5.401 6.231H2.744l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.258 5.639L18.244 2.25zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117L17.083 19.77z\"></path></svg></a><button class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-600 hover:bg-olive-100 hover:text-olive-700 transition\" aria-label=\"複製連結\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"w-4 h-4 fill-none stroke-current stroke-2\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-olive-50 py-14 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-olive-800 mb-6\">同欄目精選文章</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5\"><a class=\"group\" href=\"/blog/olive-oil-renaissance-art-science-history/\"><article class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative h-36 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"文藝復興的秘密溶劑：達文西、米開朗基羅如何用橄欖油定義了西方藝術的黃金時代 — 知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582555172866-f73bb12a2ab3?w=1200&amp;q=80\"/></div><div class=\"p-4\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-olive-800 line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-olive-600 transition-colors\">文藝復興的秘密溶劑：達文西、米開朗基羅如何用橄欖油定義了西方藝術的黃金時代</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2\">8<!-- --> 分鐘閱讀</p></div></article></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/blog/olive-oil-silk-road-trade-history/\"><article class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative h-36 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"絲路上的液態黃金：橄欖油如何在西元前連結東西方文明的貿易命脈 — 知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1569974507005-6dc61f97fb5e?w=1200&amp;q=80\"/></div><div class=\"p-4\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-olive-800 line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-olive-600 transition-colors\">絲路上的液態黃金：橄欖油如何在西元前連結東西方文明的貿易命脈</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2\">8<!-- --> 分鐘閱讀</p></div></article></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/blog/olive-tree-ancient-civilization-heritage/\"><article class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative h-36 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"橄欖樹的不死傳說：為什麼這棵三千年的古木，見證了人類最早的文明選擇？ — 知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://picture-search.skywork.ai/skills/upload/2026-04-17/7c6e503d6ec349d6aa0aa91b5e992216_9be28.png\"/></div><div class=\"p-4\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-olive-800 line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-olive-600 transition-colors\">橄欖樹的不死傳說：為什麼這棵三千年的古木，見證了人類最早的文明選擇？</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2\">9<!-- --> 分鐘閱讀</p></div></article></a></div></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--></div><footer